            I am very disappointed by
<ENAMEX TYPE="PERSON">Andrew Shuman</ENAMEX>'s "<ENAMEX TYPE="WORK_OF_ART">Weak Java</ENAMEX>." If you want to look like a propaganda organ of
<ENAMEX TYPE="ORGANIZATION">Microsoft</ENAMEX>, about the best thing you could do would be to publish an article
<NUMEX TYPE="MONEY">about</NUMEX> a very hotly contested industry issue, take <ENAMEX TYPE="ORGANIZATION">Microsoft</ENAMEX>'s side, and support
