into an operating system." This is entirely and totally wrong, and anyone
paying any attention to what's going on with <ENAMEX TYPE="ORGANIZATION">Java</ENAMEX> would know this. I am really
appalled.

            <ENAMEX TYPE="ORGANIZATION">Slate</ENAMEX> is
